title: LazyTown - You Are a Pirate Music Video
description:
Yet another music video for your viewing and listening pleasure that I can say "I spent way too much time on this"

The children's song that became an internet sensation has now received "the treatment". This should be the best version of this you'll find, unless of course you find the master copy, and even then this video includes a correction you won't find on that.

LazyTown
"You Are a Pirate"

Source:
720p YouTube FLV (Direct stream copy)
Notes:
Because this is a direct stream copy, some audio from the video not intended to be in this slightly edited version is present in the stream.
This stream is effectively mono.

Audio Stream 3: "Album FLAC"
FLAC (971kbps)
Source:
LazyTown CD Album



Overall average bitrate: 4347 kbps


The Tootie FLAC Edit is the CD album version with select sound effects, reverse-engineered from the YouTube video audio stream, mixed in.
The DVD, while available, was not utilized due to audio mastering differences.
The "LazyTown" title ending was removed, and thus the audio streams are longer than the video stream.
The original synchronization was lost over time; the frame rate was lowered to compensate.
